company_name: ALPENLANDISCHES SPEZIALFUTTERMITTELWERK DR. H. MAREK & CO. GESELLSCHAFT M.B.H.
information: The company ALPENLANDISCHES SPEZIALFUTTERMITTELWERK DR. H. MAREK & CO. GESELLSCHAFT M.B.H., is a Distributor, founded in 1945, which operates in the Feeds for animal farming industry. It is based in Wien, Austria.
